item.title: Project 4 - Implementing PICO-8 to Retro Pi
item.description: Description Quantum computer operating in superconducting qubits can go to the temperature of nearly absolute 0 degree Kelvin. It takes a huge operating cost to build and maintain its superpower. Unless you are a scientist or an engineer in an advacned reseach group or a big company like IBM, Google, Microsoft, you cannot have a taste of what it’s going on physically. It would be wonderful if you could run it on your hands.
